    "instructions": [
        "In a medium bowl, whisk together the olive oil, lime juice, garlic, soy sauce, onion powder, nutmeg, allspice, red pepper flakes, and honey. Add the chicken and toss to coat. Cover and chill for 30 minutes.",
        "While the chicken is marinating, combine the pineapple, diced onion, cilantro, jalapeno (if using), lime juice, honey, and salt in a bowl. Toss to combine and chill until ready to use.",
